<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>

<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>About - Matari Solutions LLC</title>

<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">

<style>

body{
font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
margin:0;
background:black;
}

header{
background:black;
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;
padding:15px 30px;
box-shadow:0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}


nav a{
margin-left:25px;
align-items:none;
text-decoration:underline;
color:#00a6a6;
font-weight:600;
}


.logoclear5 {
width:150px;
height:95px;
padding:50px 55px;

}

.hero{
background:Black;
color:#00a6a6;
Font-weight:Bold;
text-align:top-right;
padding:70px 55px;
}


.hero p{
font-size:18px;
margin-bottom:20px;
text-align:top-right;
}

section{
padding:0px 55px;
}

.section-title{
text-align:center;
font-size:28px;
color:#00a6a6;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

.grid{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));
gap:15px;
padding-bottom:40px;
}

.about-text{
max-width:850px;
margin:0 auto 40px auto;
color:#ddd;
font-size:17px;
line-height:1.7;
}

.gov-grid{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(200px,1fr));
gap:15px;
padding-bottom:40px;
}

.gov-card{
background:clear;
padding:25px;
border-radius:10px;
box-shadow:0 6px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
text-align:center;
}

.gov-card img{
width:100px;
height:100px;
object-fit:contain;
}

.card{
background:black;
padding:25px;
border-radius:10px;
box-shadow:0 6px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
text-align:center;
text-decoration:none;
display:block;
transition:transform 0.15s ease;
}

.card:hover{
transform:translateY(-4px);
}

.card img{
width:100px;
height:100px;
object-fit:contain;
margin-bottom:15px;
}

.card h3{
color:#00a6a6;
margin-bottom:10px;
}

.card p{
color:#333;
font-size:15px;
}

footer{
background:Black;
color:#00a6a6;
text-align:center;
padding:25px;
margin-top:40px;
}
.company-card{
background:White;
padding:25px;
border-radius:10px;
box-shadow:0 6px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
text-align:center;
text-decoration:none;
display:block;
transition:transform 0.15s ease;
}

.company-card:hover{
transform:translateY(-4px);
}

.company-card img{
width:100px;
height:100px;
object-fit:contain;
margin-bottom:15px;
}

.company-card h3{
color:#00a6a6;
margin-bottom:10px;
}

.company-card p{
color:#333;
font-size:15px;
}

@media (max-width: 768px){

header{
flex-direction:column;
align-items:flex-start;
padding:15px 20px;
}

nav a{
margin-left:0;
margin-right:20px;
font-size:14px;
}

.logoclear5{
width:110px;
height:auto;
padding:25px 20px;
}

.hero{
padding:40px 20px;
}

.hero h1{
font-size:26px;
}

.hero p{
font-size:16px;
}

section{
padding:0px 20px;
}

.section-title{
font-size:22px;
}

.grid, .gov-grid{
grid-template-columns:1fr;
}

form input, form textarea{
width:100%;
}

.contact-wrap{
padding:0 5px;
}

}
</style>
</head>


<body>

<header>


<nav>
<a href="index.html">Home</a>
<a href="about.html">About</a>
<a href="services.html">Services</a>
<a href="Contact.html">Contact</a>
</nav>

</header>

<div class="logoclear5">

<img src="logoclear5.png">


</div>

<div class="hero">

<h1></h1>
<p>Matari Solutions LLC delivers end-to-end government solutions contracting, spanning program and project management, strategic advisory, operations and support services, technology and innovation, and pricing solutions. Our team partners with agencies to plan, execute, and modernize mission-critical initiatives, ensuring every engagement is delivered with accountability, transparency, and a focus on measurable outcomes.<br></p>

<p>With 15 years of combined experience across the federal and commercial space, Matari Solutions brings proven expertise in navigating complex regulatory environments, managing large-scale programs, and building compliant, competitive pricing strategies. That depth of experience allows us to adapt quickly to evolving agency needs while maintaining the reliability and performance excellence our government and commercial partners depend on<br>
</p>

</div>


